- Fresh install xubuntu
- sudo apt update

- sudo add-apt-repository -y ppa:regolith-linux/stable
- sudo apt install i3-gaps
- logout
- login dengan session i3


- sudo apt install git
- git clone https://github.com/desdrianton/my-linux-notes
- symlink my-linux-notes/dot-config ke ~/.config untuk directory
	- i3
	- htop
	- pcmanfm
	- polybar

- sudo apt install geany pcmanfm lxappearance arc-theme arc-icon papirus-icon-theme theme rofi nitrogen neofetch scrot flameshot grub-customizer dunst

========================================================= Ricing (theme)
- lxappearance
	- Pilih theme
	- Pilih icon
	
- geany
	- Pilih theme
	- line height => 2;2

- Wallpaper
	- Pilih wallpaper dgn nitrogen
	- Ketika next restart, nitrogen akan di load ulang oleh script di git


- timedatectl set-local-rtc 1
